name: FindFlightInformation
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: flight planner
des: This Alexa skill will allow its users to find out the latest information on flights all around the world. They can find the cheapest possible flights between two locations and date(s). They can also find timetable information on flights that are arriving or departing from specific airports. This is all done by using APIs provided by Skyscanner and Aviation-Edge.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
